Instalacion Windows

Instalar xampp o un gestor de base de datos
Instalar composer
Instalar Node js
Instalar git bash

Instalar composer
en la terminal ponemos

composer create-project laravel/laravel example-app

https://laravel.com/docs/10.x/installation

instalar laravel 
composer global require laravel/installer:^5.4

si da error quitamos la version 

composer global require laravel/installer

crear un nuevo proyecto

laravel new blog 


Crear Controlador

php artisan make:controller NombreController

crear una migracion

php artisan make:migration create_nombre_table

hacer la migracion 

php artisan migrate


crear modelo 

php artisna make:model Nombre -m 

o

php artisna make:model Nombre -a


<link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ asset('css/basicos.css') }}">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ asset('css/normalize.css') }}">



iniciar servidor

php artisan serve

instalacion en linux

instalar composer

php -r "copy('https://getcomposer.org/installer', 'composer-setup.php');"
php -r "if (hash_file('sha384', 'composer-setup.php') === 'a5c698ffe4b8e849a443b120cd5ba38043260d5c4023dbf93e1558871f1f07f58274fc6f4c93bcfd858c6bd0775cd8d1') { echo 'Installer verified'; } else { echo 'Installer corrupt'; unlink('composer-setup.php'); } echo PHP_EOL;"
php composer-setup.php
php -r "unlink('composer-setup.php');"
sudo mv composer.phar /usr/local/bin/composer

instalar php o xxampp

sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install php php-cli php-mbstring unzip

instalar laravel

composer global require laravel/installer

crear nuevo proyecto

laravel new nombre_del_proyecto
